The '''Tagge Mining Company''' was a subsidiary company of [[Tagge Company/Legends|Tagge Company]].<ref name="HSCS" /> They maintained operations on [[Besero/Legends|Besero]],<ref name="RPG2" /> [[Drarn]], [[Terig]],<ref name="P170" /> and [[Krann]].<ref name="FKM" /> They manufactured the [[AEA-500 mineral extractor]].<ref name="GFT" />

